'''Pinkie's Gala Fantasy Song'''是[[The Ticket Master]]內的一首[[歌曲|歌曲]]，由 [[碧琪]]主唱，她幻想著參加[[大奔騰慶典]]當她看到[[紫悅]]有兩張票。紫悅在[[Friendship is Magic, part 1|第一集]]的象牙塔也會出現在碧琪後面的背景。[http://www.hasbro.com/mylittlepony/en_US/play/details.cfm?guid=7E2366FB-5056-900B-106A-C25FB3EE3840&src=endeca Hasbro's website]有提供這首歌的影片。這首歌是由Daniel Ingram跟Steffan Andrews共同編曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/steffan.andrews.music/posts/251648394955121|title=Steffan Andrews answers a question on Facebook|date=2012-08-01|accessdate=2012-08-01}}</ref>

